title: UWFox Tree Survey Data from GEO 106
name: UWFox Tree Survey Data from GEO 106
description: This is a point shapefile mapping the locations of trees on the campus of the University of Wisconsin-Fox Valley in Menasha, Wisconsin.  The trees were inventories with a number of attributes and mapped as part of the campus's initiative to become TreeCampus USA certified.
